question: What fast food restaurant is available as I head towards Gordon-Conwell theological Seminary, South Hamilton, MA within 150 kilometers from Wolf Hill Forest Preserve, Smithfield, RI?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-71.539863 41.898564)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-70.843039 42.606219)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'fast_food'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-71.539863 41.898564)',4326)::geography, 150000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-71.539863 41.898564)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);

answers.opening_hours: "60 prior to first flight till 30 prior to last flight"

answers.description: Menu at https://places.singleplatform.com/greco-11/menu Available on some food delivery services.

[3].display_name: Wolf Hill Forest Preserve, Smithfield, RI

[4].display_name: Gordon-Conwell Theological Seminary, South Hamilton, MA
